---
import AccessRequestForm from './AccessRequestForm.astro';

const smallQuotes = [
  {
    text: 'Our team has become much more comfortable with us going toward AI native.',
    author: 'Private beta tester',
    context: 'On team-wide impact',
  },
  {
    text: 'That guidance actually changed how we\'re approaching the decision. It kept us from uprooting everything we\'re doing with our internal systems.',
    author: 'Private beta tester',
    context: 'On asking AmbitiousOS whether to switch platforms',
  },
  {
    text: 'I tried to give the excuse that I\'ve never coded anything. AmbitiousOS wouldn\'t let me off the hook. The answer was just build.',
    author: 'Private beta tester',
    context: 'On getting started with Claude Code',
  },
];
---

<section class="section-padding" id="testimonials">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary text-center mb-12">
      What beta testers are saying
    </h2>

    <!-- Featured testimonial -->
    <div class="glass-card glass-card-accent p-8 sm:p-10 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <blockquote class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-text-primary leading-relaxed italic">
          &ldquo;I've always been looking over the fence at other people in the AI space.
          With AmbitiousOS, I'm able to be a part of this agentic AI revolution,
          rather than watch it happening.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-text-primary leading-relaxed italic">
          &ldquo;I would love to be able to talk to you about this all the time.
          The fact that I can take your best thinking and your best research and have that
          conversation, and get really compelling, thoughtful, articulate answers.
          It's just been a tremendous unlock for me, and it's really given me
          the confidence to become a builder.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <footer class="pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
          <cite class="not-italic text-text-secondary font-medium">Private beta tester</cite>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-3">
        <div class="use-case-callout">
          <span class="use-case-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏢</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">
            His team was about to rip out their existing systems and move everything to a new platform.
            He asked AmbitiousOS for guidance, and the answer changed their entire approach:
            apply AI to what you already have, don't uproot everything. That advice redirected their strategy.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="use-case-callout">
          <span class="use-case-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔨</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">
            He'd never written a line of code. He asked AmbitiousOS how to start with Claude Code
            and tried to give the excuse that he wasn't technical. The answer? Just build. Within hours
            he was learning to code. A bridge he says he never would have crossed without AmbitiousOS.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quote wall -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      {smallQuotes.map((q) => (
        <div class="glass-card p-6">
          <blockquote>
            {q.context && (
              <p class="text-text-muted text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 font-medium">{q.context}</p>
            )}
            <p class="text-text-primary leading-relaxed italic mb-4">
              &ldquo;{q.text}&rdquo;
            </p>
            <footer>
              <cite class="not-italic text-sm text-text-muted">&mdash; {q.author}</cite>
            </footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-10">
      <button type="button" class="btn-primary" data-open-form="testimonials-access-form" onclick="if(typeof plausible==='function')plausible('CTA Click',{props:{location:'testimonials',type:'request-access'}})">
        Join the beta
        <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto mt-4">
      <AccessRequestForm id="testimonials-access-form" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .use-case-callout {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(2, 69, 54, 0.08);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(2, 69, 54, 0.15);
  }

  .use-case-icon {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
</style>
